{"id":149557,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/阿富汗的暴力斗争还在继续/","date":"2011-05-03T13:00:22Z","modified":"2011-05-03T13:00:22Z","title":"阿富汗的暴力斗争还在继续","content":"<div>\n<p>喀布尔</p>\n<p>本·拉登被美国特种部队击毙一天后，阿富汗安全力量在通往巴基斯坦边境地带打死或打伤25名外籍反叛武装人员。当地政治家称，死者中包括阿拉伯人、车臣人以及巴基斯坦人。目前，边境检查得到加强。本·拉登曾得到阿富汗塔利班的多年支持。另据报道，北约直升机在阿富汗南部空袭过程中，至少炸死8名阿富汗保安人员。当地警方说，他们正在为北约护送物品的途中。可能北约士兵将他们误认为反叛力量，从而导致向他们开火。</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15046026%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E7%9A%84%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%96%97%E4%BA%89%E8%BF%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[11392]}